T02TD2248E:137b-1: ma h'a y'a na bing sha ti //
T02TD2248E:137b-3: theg pa chen po nyi shu pa //
T02TD2248E:137b-4: snying po'i sku la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2248E:137b-6: rnam pa kun gyi mchog ldan pa //
T02TD2248E:137b-7: mtshan nyid med cing 'dus ma byas //
T02TD2248E:138a-2: 'di ni chos dang longs spyod sbrul //
T02TD2248E:138a-3: snying po de yi rang bzhin pas //
T02TD2248E:138a-4: de la 'di mthong ldan pa yis //
T02TD2248E:138a-5: yang dag rdzogs pa'i byang chub 'grub //
T02TD2248E:138a-6: 'di la mthong bar gyur pa yis //
T02TD2248E:138a-7: sgro ma btags pas lhag par mthong //
T02TD2248E:138a-8: gsang sngags theg pa'i rjes 'brangs nas ;
T02TD2248E:138a-9: / de 'dir da ltar bshad par bya //
T02TD2248E:138a-10: sna tshogs rtog pa'i gzhung ni med //
T02TD2248E:138a-11: chad par sems pa'ang med pa ste //
T02TD2248E:138a-12: rtag dang chad pa'ang gnyis ka med //
T02TD2248E:138a-13: gnyis po med pas gnyis min te //
T02TD2248E:138a-14: mtha' bzhi rnam grol de nyid ni //
T02TD2248E:138a-15: de nyid rig pa mkhas pas shes //
T02TD2248E:138a-16: mtha' bzhi rnam par dag pa nyid //
T02TD2248E:138a-17: mtha' bzhi la ni rnam par brten //
T02TD2248E:138a-18: nam mkha' dang mnyam zhi ba dang //
T02TD2248E:138a-19: thog ma dbus dang tha ma spangs //
T02TD2248E:138a-20: bsam gyis mi khyab sems nyid ni //
T02TD2248E:138a-21: dngos po kun gyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2248E:138a-22: 'gro ba ro gcig par rtogs na //
T02TD2248E:138a-23: rnyog pa med cing 'od gsal ba'o //
T02TD2248E:138a-24: kun du rtog pas 'jigs med na //
T02TD2248E:138a-25: ji ltar bde ba khyod gnas byos //
T02TD2248E:138a-26: byang chub nyon mongs tha dad med //
T02TD2248E:138a-27: nyon mongs byang chub las mi 'byung //
T02TD2248E:138a-28: 'khrul pas nyon mongs rtogs pa ste //
T02TD2248E:138a-29: 'khrul pa'i ngo bo dri ma med //
T02TD2248E:138a-30: lus kyi las su spyod lam ste //
T02TD2248E:138a-31: ngag gi las ni chos ston te //
T02TD2248E:138a-32: yid kyi las su yang dag 'dzin //
T02TD2248E:138a-33: rnam par mi rtog blo ldan pa'o //
T02TD2248E:138a-35: sgyu mas sgyu ma mi bya ste //
T02TD2248E:138a-36: sgyu ma rmongs pas 'khrul pa che //
T02TD2248E:138a-38: ji ltar rang bzhin rnam shes na //
T02TD2248E:138a-39: sangs rgyas la sogs bsdus pa ste //
T02TD2248E:138a-40: kun nas kun du longs spyod na //
T02TD2248E:138a-41: de nyid rig par rab tu 'grub //
T02TD2248E:138a-42: chos kyi phung po stong phrag gis //
T02TD2248E:138a-43: rtog pa zhes bya stong pa nyid //
T02TD2248E:138a-44: rtag pa 'di ni dpyad pas min //
T02TD2248E:138a-45: bla mas dpyad pa min par 'gyur //
T02TD2248E:138a-46: skyes bu rnam rtog bral ba ni //
T02TD2248E:138a-47: rnam kun bde ba'i de nyid do //
T02TD2248E:138a-48: stong nyid bde ba'i de nyid min ;
T02TD2248E:138a-49: / bsam mi khyab min bde ba min //
T02TD2248E:138a-50: des na sangs rgyas sgro ma btags //
T02TD2248E:138a-51: de ni don dam mthong ba med //
T02TD2248E:138a-52: gang la spyod pa ji ltar bde //
T02TD2248E:138a-53: de lta rig pa mthong ba med //
T02TD2248E:138a-54: gnyis su med pa gnyis med min //
T02TD2248E:138a-55: byang chub dag pa'i mtshan nyid med //
T02TD2248E:138b-0: @138b rnam pa thams cad rtogs pa'o //
T02TD2248E:138b-1: ji ltar gsungs pa dang po'i las //
T02TD2248E:138b-2: rnal 'byor kun gyi bya ba yin //
T02TD2248E:138b-3: stong dang snying rje dbyer med pa //
T02TD2248E:138b-4: de ni sangs rgyas ye shes 'dod //
T02TD2248E:138b-5: stong las snying rje gzhan min te //
T02TD2248E:138b-6: snying rje yi ni ming gzhan yin //
T02TD2248E:138b-7: bdag gis 'dus byas su mi brjod//
T02TD2248E:138b-8: brjod pa zung du 'jug par ro //
T02TD2248E:138b-9: bum pa la sogs 'dzin gang la //
T02TD2248E:138b-10: rnal 'byor kun gyi bsam gtan bya //
T02TD2248E:138b-12: rnam pa kun gyi lus gcig pa'o //
T02TD2248E:138b-13: 'dus ma byas sems chos yin te //
T02TD2248E:138b-14: rtogs pa'i longs spyod rdzogs mtshan nyid //
T02TD2248E:138b-15: sna tshogs sems ni sbrul pa'o //
T02TD2248E:138b-16: gnyug ma kun gyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD2248E:138b-17: de ltar 'di yis thob pa ni //
T02TD2248E:138b-18: bsod nams ldan pa'i bsod nams kyis //
T02TD2248E:138b-19: de ni 'jig rten ma lus pa //
T02TD2248E:138b-20: sangs rgyas byang chub thob par shog / theg pa chen po nyi shu pa slob dpon gnyis med rdo rjes mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD2248E:138b-22: // / pa ri pa ta pradzny'a sha ra sa ma dhya na /
T02TD2248E:138b-23: rgya gar gyi mkhan po de b'a ka ra tsandra dang /
T02TD2248E:138b-24: bod kyi lo ts'a ba dge slong sh'a kya brtson 'grus kyis bsgyur cing zhus te gtan la dbab pa'o//
